54.9	Day_of_Ashura	Day of Ashura	The Day of Ashura (Arabic: ‎ ; Persian: عاشورا; Turkish: Aşure Günü) is on the 10th day of Muharram in the Islamic calendar and marks the climax of the Remembrance of Muharram.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6a/Ashura_Hardoi_2011.jpg/225px-Ashura_Hardoi_2011.jpg
